  GAME INFORMATION:
 -------------------
  Set in a fantasy interpretation of ancient India, Unrest is an adventure 
  RPG focused on story and choices. Play as five ordinary people who are 
  struggling to get by in the famine-stricken city-state of Bhimra.

  Brave poverty, disease, treason, political and social upheaval. Face unique 
  burdens and gripping dilemmas as you struggle to survive in each chapter...
  but choices made to help one character may well make life harder for another.
  
  In Unrest, there are no heroes of legend, there is no mystical quest, and 
  fate has not chosen you. You're on your own.
